<div><p>Figure <ref type="figure">1</ref> shows as an example raw data measured by a 2D detector and projected to the H0L and K0L planes. In Fig. <ref type="figure">2</ref> we present a preliminary comparison of the measured and simulated <rs type="funder">CTR</rs> scans.</p></div>
